      "span_text": "Recently, multiparticle cryoelectron microscopy and single-molecule FRET investigations of the mammalian pre-translocation complex conducted in collaboration with Christian Spahn's laboratory revealed critical distinctions in the structural and energetic features of bacterial and mammalian ribosomes, providing a mechanistic basis for divergent translation regulation strategies and species-specific antibiotic action [CITATION_1] ."
